<div style="background-color: #202020" data-bb-type="screen">
	<div data-bb-type="title" data-bb-caption="Profit and Loss"></div>


	<div style="background-color: #202020" data-bb-type="round-panel"> 
		<div style="color: white;">
		<h2>Cost price:</h2>

		<i>The amount on which an object is purchased(C.P). </i>
 
		</div>
	</div>

<div style="background-color: #202020" data-bb-type="round-panel"> 
		<div style="color: white;">
		<h2>Selling Price:</h2>

		<i> The amount on which an object is  sold(S.P).</i>
 
		</div>
	</div>
<div style="background-color: #202020" data-bb-type="round-panel"> 
		<div style="color: white;">
		<h2>Gain</h2>

		<i>the additional amount which we get when we sell a product greater than Cost price. </i>
 
		</div>
	</div>
<div style="background-color: #202020" data-bb-type="round-panel"> 
		<div style="color: white;">
		<h2>Loss</h2>

		<i> The product price(S.P) is less than Cost Price(C.P)</i>
 
		</div>
	</div>
<div style="background-color: #202020" data-bb-type="round-panel"> 
		<div style="color: white;">
		<h2>Gain and Loss</h2>

		<i>Gain = S.P - C.P <br/>Loss = C.p - S.P </i>
 
		</div>
	</div>
<div style="background-color: #202020" data-bb-type="round-panel"> 
		<div style="color: white;">
		<h2>In percentage</h2>

		<i>Gain in % = (Gain * 100) / Original price or C.P <br/>Loss in % = (Loss * 100) / Original price or C.P </i>
 
		</div>
	</div>
<div style="background-color: #202020" data-bb-type="round-panel"> 
		<div style="color: white;">
		<h2>Selling Price</h2>

		<i>S.P = ( (100 + Gain in %) / 100 ) * C.P </i> <br />
		<b>or</b> <br />
		<i> </i>
 
		</div>
	</div>
<div style="background-color: #202020" data-bb-type="round-panel"> 
		<div style="color: white;">
		<h2></h2>

		<i> </i>
 
